member.summary:
Gets data when the caller's range is contained by one of the current validations that is returned.
Each rectangle of the range (a collection) must be contained; 
otherwise, throws an exception.

Gets the value of the specified range as a string, double, bool", object[,] or null; 
or sets the value of the specified cell as a string, double, int32, int64, 
int16, bool, , object[,] or null.
